snippet.title: Super Mini Mart 2022 Teaser
snippet.description:
Support us via wishlisting the game! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1914060/Super_Mini_Mart/

Super Mini Mart is planned to release on PC in 2023.

Super Mini Mart is a charmingly carefree single-player management game in which you are tasked with handling all the day-to-day activities of an up-and-coming convenience store. Manage products, create promotions and fulfill the needs of every unique customer, to become the most thriving supermarket in town!

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Super_Mini_Mart
Join our Discord Community: https://discord.gg/zXU6jCTBRY
~
Video Edit by Katherine Leiter (https://piranhartist.wixsite.com/portfolio)
Music and SFX by Jacob Lincke (https://jacob-lincke.com/)
